00076 {
00077     ListBaseIterator *internal = iter->internal;
00078     Sequence *seq = (Sequence*)internal->link;
00079 
00080     if (seq->seqbase.first)
00081         internal->link = (Link*)seq->seqbase.first;
00082     else if (seq->next)
00083         internal->link = (Link*)seq->next;
00084     else {
00085         internal->link = NULL;
00086 
00087         do {
00088             seq = seq->tmp; /* XXX - seq's don't reference their parents! */
00089             if (seq && seq->next) {
00090                 internal->link = (Link*)seq->next;
00091                 break;
00092             }
00093         } while (seq);
00094     }
00095 
00096     iter->valid = (internal->link != NULL);

00667 static void rna_SequenceEditor_overlay_lock_set(PointerRNA *ptr, int value)
00668 {
00669     Scene *scene = ptr->id.data;
00670     Editing *ed = seq_give_editing(scene, FALSE);
00671 
00672     if (ed == NULL)
00673         return;
00674 
00675     /* convert from abs to relative and back */
00676     if ((ed->over_flag & SEQ_EDIT_OVERLAY_ABS) == 0 && value) {
00677         ed->over_cfra = scene->r.cfra + ed->over_ofs;
00678         ed->over_flag |= SEQ_EDIT_OVERLAY_ABS;
00679     }
00680     else if ((ed->over_flag & SEQ_EDIT_OVERLAY_ABS) && !value) {
00681         ed->over_ofs = ed->over_cfra - scene->r.cfra;
00682         ed->over_flag &= ~SEQ_EDIT_OVERLAY_ABS;
00683     }
00684 }
